"On a more personal note, I have mentioned in previous articles that Reddit shadow banned me breifly about two years ago. A few months ago, I was also shadow banned on Hacker News. Multiple moats failed. This was no accident. Takes time to build up such incompetence.

FIX IT! NOW!

FIND THE SMART PEOPLE WHOSE HANDS ARE CLEAN.

Cuz nothing is written in stone....

If little Taiwan has character, every man, woman, child on that island is well armed, and the Taiwanese military has a well developed plan for retaking the mainland.

Now US could help - but mostly with fuckery. By selling pirate permits to assholes who like to fight. 

Still, at the end of the day....it's your China Taiwan. You should take it back if those mainland punks visit you. Those commissars would look nice hanging from lamp posts.....And they have been asking for it.

And well, if you need mercenaries - biggest bazaar is here. Might be smart to offer them something new. Like those 72 virgins up front? There would be takers.
Russian & Mongol mercenaries could be bought too.  

Nothing has changed. People like this still exist....Ignore the media.
